(3, 'fa fa-star', 'Technical Advisors', '&#x3C;p&#x3E;In addition to a panel of eminent consultants and advisors, we have a dedicated pool of trained surveyors and investigators, working under the guidance of professional managers. Some of the key professionals and advisors are listed below:&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. B. George (Ex-Chief Mining Geologist, Indian Bureau of Mines):&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; M. Tech (Applied Geology), Post Graduate Diploma in Photo Geology and Remote Sensing in Applied Geology. Has 47 years of experience and expertise in geologic appraisal, exploration, assessment of mineral reserves, study of economic mining potential, feasibility studies etc. for mining companies and organizations in public and private sector. He has also undertaken notable assignments in geological mapping and exploration of iron ore, chromite, manganese, limestone etc.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. Pramod Kumar Jain:&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; M.Sc. Geology (gold medalist), MBA (Marketing). Has over 19 years of experience in exploration of minerals, sales and marketing and preparation of tender documents and award of contracts.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Prof. K. C. Sahu (Ex-Vice President, New India Mining Corporation):&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; (Ex-Vice President, New India Mining Corporation) B.Tech.(Earth Sciences), M.Tech. (Earth Sciences) IIT Kharagpur, Ph.D. University of Sheffield (UK). Has 37 years of experience as a geologist expert in earth sciences. He Specialized in geochemistry and application of geochemical principles to environmental problems like heavy metal pollution to air, water, soil, sediment and biota.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. Jalil Ahmad (Ex-Chief General Manager, Coal India Ltd.):&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; Post Graduate Diploma in Industrial management, Mines Manager Certificate. Has more than 35 years of experience in Coal India Limited, with expertise in opencast mining and underground mines, maintaining environment of the surrounding mines area as per government norms and land rehabilitation.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. Bhagwan Singh:&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; B.Tech. (Chemical), M.Tech. (Chemical). Has 23 years of experience in the Central Mine Planning and Design Institute Ltd. and expertise in the planning and designing of project report as well as the overall supervision for various coal preparation and utilization projects.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Dr. Madhusudan Patil:&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; M.Sc. (Geology), Ph.D. (photo geology and geomorphology). Has 46 years of experience as a geologist in exploratory and development wells in different oil fields, sand geometry and depositional environments on geological and geophysical data.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. Prabhat Kumar Chatterjee:&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; B.E. (Mining), Mines Manager Certificate, GoI. He has 36 years of experience in Coal India Limited and has expertise in ventilation and other mine development planning and execution work, productivity, profitability, safety and welfare of mining areas.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. Devraj Barua (Ex- Environment Officer, NHDC):&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; M.Sc. (Environmental Sciences), M. Tech. (Energy and Environment Management). Has 12 years of expertise in preparing detailed project reports for hydro power projects and implementing environmental safeguard measures for hydroelectric projects.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. Satish Chandra Srivastava (Ex-Geologist, Geological Survey of India):&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; M.Sc. (Geology). Has 32 years of experience with GSI and expertise in the field of Engineering Geology and Laboratory Geo-techniques, traverse mapping, geological mapping, approach audits, exploratory drifts etc.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Prof. (Dr.) Amarendra Kumar Sinha (Ex-Professor, Department of Geology, University of Rajasthan):&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; M.Sc. (Geology), M. Phil, Ph.D. (Geology). Have 36 years of teaching experience and over 25 years of research experience. His area of expertise is geo-environmental studies using geospatial tools, geo-hazard studies, groundwater resource mapping, resource evaluation and environmental monitoring through satellite imagery.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\n                        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Mr. A. K. Sachdeva:&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; B.E. (Mechanical), MBA, PG Diploma in Construction Management. Has 37 years of rich and varied experience in hydro power development industry with expertise in overall management of hydroelectric projects in different stages and phases, design and engineering, research and development, procurement and contract management etc.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;', 'active', '2023-05-10 10:05:49', 0, NULL, NULL),
