(6, 'Global warming set to break key 1.5C limit for first time', 'Global warming set to break key 1.5C limit for first time', 1, 'yes', '1685343626142-890070818.jpg', '1685343626136-111607157.jpg', '1686547498698-168437805.pdf', '&#x3C;div data-component=&#x22;text-block&#x22; class=&#x22;ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0&#x22; style=&#x22;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); letter-spacing: normal;&#x22;&#x3E;&#x3C;div class=&#x22;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1&#x22; style=&#x22;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;&#x22;&#x3E;&#x3C;p class=&#x22;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00&#x22; style=&#x22;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#x22;&#x3E;&#x3C;b class=&#x22;ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3&#x22; style=&#x22;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#x22;&#x3E;Our overheating world is likely to break a key temperature limit for the first time over the next few years, scientists predict.&#x3C;/b&#x3E;&#x3C;/p&#x3E;&#x3C;/div&#x3E;&#x3C;/div&#x3E;&#x3C;div data-component=&#x22;text-block&#x22; class=&#x22;ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0&#x22; style=&#x22;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: