(15, 'NOC Pollution Control Board', 'noc-pollution-control-board', 5, '\r\n&#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-page&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;div class=&#x22;container&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-12&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;ab-sec1 ab-sec-ser1&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;h2&#x3E;File for NOC from Pollution Control Board with GRC India&#x3C;/h2&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;p&#x3E;To operate an industry, manufacturers are required to secure NOC from the requisite pollution control board. The central Environmental Protection board and pollution control authorities have categorised the diverse industries based on the amount of pollution emitted. This categorisation of industries is applicable under the Water (Prevention &#x26;amp; Control of Pollution) Act, 1974 and Air (Prevention &#x26;amp; Control of Pollution) Act, 1981.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;zoom-in-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/gr8.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-down-left&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;Categories of Industries under Pollution Control Board&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;ul&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Orange Category&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Red Category&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Green Category&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;White Category&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/ul&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Industries that fall in the red, orange or green category are required to secure their CTO/CTE from the pollution control authorities. It is mandatory for all the industries under these categories to get NOC from the Pollution Control Board.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Industries under the white category do not require CTO&#x3C;a href=&#x22;https://www.grc-india.com/services/cto-cte-pollution-control-board&#x22; target=&#x22;_blank&#x22;&#x3E;/CTE from the pollution control board online.&#x3C;/a&#x3E;&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;  \r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row mt-5&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-down&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Compliance executives at GRC India extend services to file your &#x3C;b&#x3E;NOC from Pollution Control Board in Delhi NCR&#x3C;/b&#x3E;. We assist manufacturers to secure their NOC under the Water (Prevention &#x26;amp; Control of Pollution) Act, 1974 and Air (Prevention &#x26;amp; Control of Pollution) Act, 1981.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Based on the revised classification of industries by the Central Pollution Control Board as of February 2, 2019, GRC India assists in securing NOC to the below-listed industries-&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;ul&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;li&#x3E;Red Category- Hotels, restaurants, clubs and lodges with overall wastewater generation (100 KLD or more).&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;li&#x3E;Orange Category- Hotels ( &#x26;gt; 3 Star) or hotels ( with more than 20 but less than 100) rooms and have a coal/oil fired boiler.&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;li&#x3E;Green Category- Hotels up to 20 rooms without boilers, overall wastewater generation( &#x26;lt; 10 KLD) and no hazardous waste generation.&#x3C;/li&#x3E; \r\n        &#x3C;/ul&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;  \r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/gr9.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E; \r\n  &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-page1&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;div class=&#x22;container&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;&#x3C;span style=&#x22;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x26;quot;Segoe UI&#x26;quot;, Roboto, &#x26;quot;Helvetica Neue&#x26;quot;, Arial, &#x26;quot;Noto Sans&#x26;quot;, &#x26;quot;Liberation Sans&#x26;quot;, sans-serif, &#x26;quot;Apple Color Emoji&#x26;quot;, &#x26;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&#x26;quot;, &#x26;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&#x26;quot;, &#x26;quot;Noto Color Emoji&#x26;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.00938em;&#x22;&#x3E;GRC India: Helping You Grow With Sustainable Solutions&#x3C;/span&#x3E;&#x3C;br&#x3E;&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;GRC India is setting an example amongst ecological consulting firms in India by yielding an opportunity to companies towards working on an integrated approach for the conservation of ecology and biodiversity. Our organisation stands dedicated to providing assistance in minimising the negative effects of human activities on the environment. We strive to put all our knowledge and experience into assisting our clients to manage their projects&#x27; development without disrupting the ecosystems. Contact us to know more about our ecological &#x26;amp; biodiversity studies.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;zoom-in-left&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/gr19.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;/div&#x3E;', '1648282680907-218795808.jpg', '1648282680899-667862265.jpg', 'active', '2022-03-26 13:48:00', 1, '2024-03-11 11:54:05', 1, 'NOC from pollution control board Delhi NCR - GRC India', 'We at GRC India, provide a hassle-free path to securing NOC from the Pollution Control Board. Get swift and efficient approvals with our expert advice and guidance.  ', 'NOC from pollution control board, NOC from pollution control board Delhi NCR'),
(16, 'CTO & CTE Pollution Control Board', 'cto-cte-pollution-control-board', 2, '&#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-page&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;div class=&#x22;container&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-12&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;ab-sec1 ab-sec-ser1&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;h2&#x3E;CTE &#x26;amp; CTO - An Overview&#x3C;/h2&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;p&#x3E;Industries dealing with pollutants and hazardous wastes require consent from the authority to carry out operations. Any form of manufacturing industry and commercial establishments require secure consent from the requisite pollution control board.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;p&#x3E;If the consent expires, it is mandatory for a manufacturer to apply for renewal with the pollution control board. Industries require two forms of No Objection Certificates (NOC) to start their operations. We at GRC India are here to assist you in securing the two types of NOCs for your industry, i.e. CTO and CTE.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;zoom-in-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/gr12.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up-left&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;CTE or Consent to Establish&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Consent To Establish is the form of compliance required to establish or carry out manufacturing industrial operations. Any industry, operation or process discharging sewerage or trade effluent to the environment or likely to emit air pollution into the atmosphere are required to obtain CTE from the respective state pollution control board.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;At GRC India, our team of compliance executives help you apply for &#x3C;b&#x3E;CTE from the pollution control board online.&#x3C;/b&#x3E;&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;CTO or Consent To Operate&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Another form of compliance to secure NOC is Consent To Operate. Manufacturers are required to secure this consent to ensure their industry is maintaining standards related to the operations. It is mandatory for all industries to get this consent to operate.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;At GRC India, we extend our services for &#x3C;b&#x3E;CTO from pollution control board online registration.&#x3C;/b&#x3E;&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;CTO and CTE are permissions required by industries from the State Pollution Control Board under sections 25/26 of the Water (Prevention &#x26;amp; Control of Pollution) Act, 1974 &#x26;amp; section 21 of the Air (Prevention &#x26;amp; Control of Pollution) Act, 1981. &#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;  \r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E; \r\n  &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-page1&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;div class=&#x22;container&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;List of Industries That Require CTO/CTE From Pollution Control Board&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;ul&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Manufacturing Industries&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Health Care Sectors and Institutions&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Industries in the Sectors related E-Waste Management&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Solid Waste Management Industries&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Industries in Hazardous Waste Management&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Battery waste management entities&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Plastic waste management entities&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;li&#x3E;Bio-Medical waste management industries.&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/ul&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;Secure Your CTO/ CTE with GRC India!&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;GRC India comprises a team of skilled and experienced experts working towards providing optimal solutions to add value to your business. At GRC, we extend our services to register your entity and &#x3C;a href=&#x22;https://www.grc-india.com/services/noc-pollution-control-board&#x22; target=&#x22;_blank&#x22;&#x3E;NOC from the Pollution Control Board Delhi NCR&#x3C;/a&#x3E;. We constantly monitor the process and support you until the certificate is delivered.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;&#x3C;strong&#x3E;Contact us&#x3C;/strong&#x3E; to apply for your NOC today.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;zoom-in-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/comp5.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;/div&#x3E;', '1648283630349-576529577.jpg', '1648283630345-210212070.jpg', 'active', '2022-03-26 14:03:50', 1, '2024-02-28 13:55:38', 1, 'CTO & CTE from pollution control board online registration -GRC India', 'GRC India- Streamlining your CTE from the Pollution Control Board online and simplifying the online registration of your CTO from the Pollution Control Board. Trust our expertise to get environmental compliance with ease.', 'CTE from pollution control board online, cto from pollution control board online registration'),
(17, 'Research And Training', 'research-and-training', 7, '&#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-page&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;div class=&#x22;container&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/gr14.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-left&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;ul&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;li&#x3E;Conducting research studies on specific subject related to Pollution Control Technology, Survey and Inventory, Chemical Analysis, and Feasibility Studies etc.&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;li&#x3E;Conducting training programme, awareness programs and workshops for Capability Development of Managers and Environmentalists&#x3C;/li&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/ul&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;  \r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E; \r\n  &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;/div&#x3E;', '1648283822668-390211540.jpg', '1648283822663-332338327.jpg', 'active', '2022-03-26 14:07:02', 1, '2022-05-03 14:37:34', 1, 'research-and-training', 'research-and-training', 'research-and-training'),
(18, 'Half Yearly Compliance Report', 'half-yearly-compliance-report', 4, '&#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-page&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n  &#x3C;div class=&#x22;container&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-12&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up-right&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;ab-sec1 ab-sec-ser1&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;h2&#x3E;Obtain Your Half-Yearly Compliance Report from GRC India&#x3C;/h2&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;p&#x3E;GRC India extends services for half-yearly compliance reports to projects as a part of the post environmental clearance monitoring process. It is mandatory for project management to submit a half-yearly compliance report in respect of the prior environmental clearance terms and conditions in hard &#x26;amp; soft copies to the concerned regulatory authority on 1st June and 1st December of each calendar year.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;p&#x3E;All the half-yearly compliance reports submitted by the project management will be public documents. Copies of the compliance reports shall be provided to any person on application to the concerned authority. The latest half-yearly compliance reports will also be displayed on the website of the concerned regulatory authority.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n    &#x3C;div class=&#x22;row&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22; dataaos=&#x22;fade-up-left&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-img&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n          &#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://api.grc-india.com/uploads/images/comp1.jpg&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;col-md-6&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;div class=&#x22;about-inner&#x22;&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;h3&#x3E;Our Vision: Add Value to the Client&#x2019;s Project through Our Services&#x3C;/h3&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;GRC India, highly trusted as one of the country&#x27;s leading &#x3C;a href=&#x22;https://www.grc-india.com/services/advisory-services&#x22; target=&#x22;_blank&#x22;&#x3E;environmental management consultants&#x3C;/a&#x3E;, is an organisation with a team of multidisciplinary experts (in-house and empanelled) working with persistence and dedication to providing optimal solutions for all EIA needs. It aims to make the post-environmental monitoring process hassle-free for the clients. Our team of experienced professionals has successfully culminated numerous projects within limited time frames to ensure quality services to our clients.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;Combining our knowledge with unrivalled experience, we offer services to both national and international customers to meet their requirements. Our organisation is a leading Environmental Consultancy for all Environment Management Services in India.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;p&#x3E;We promise to deliver cost-effective solutions to help you obtain your half-yearly compliance report. Contact us to know more about our compliance report services.&#x3C;/p&#x3E;\r\n        &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n      &#x3C;/div&#x3E;  \r\n    &#x3C;/div&#x3E; \r\n  &#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n&#x3C;/div&#x3E;\r\n', '1648284242722-191086561.jpg', '1648284242719-76487439.jpg', 'active', '2022-03-26 14:14:02', 1, '2024-02-28 14:11:06', 1, 'Half yearly compliance Report - GRC India', 'Trust GRC India for comprehensive, on-time, half-yearly compliance reports. Your reliable partner for regulatory adherence. ', 'Half Yearly Compliance Report');
